{"type":"message","id":"7877612f","parentId":"b814ff59","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:59:40.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Voy a crear MEMORY.md y dejar esa nota persistente ahГӯ, con referencia al playbook.\n","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c2a6d9221c819180f0847231ad92d6\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_X3yN9Hqr50AP8At3PGoazCYd|fc_07843e13d03825ba0169c2a6d9bd408191be54963e168606ec","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/Gustavo/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","content":"# MEMORY.md\n\n## OperaciГіn / OpenClaw\n\n- Para crear nuevos agentes aislados en OpenClaw, existe un playbook replicable en `workspace/agents-setup-playbook.md`.\n- Caso base ya implementado: **Hestia**.\n- PatrГіn recordatorio:\n  1. `cmd /c openclaw agents add <id>`\n  2. copiar auth desde `main`\n  3. no configurar canales en el wizard si la ruta aГәn no estГЎ clara\n  4. personalizar `workspace-<id>/IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md` y `SOUL.md`\n  5. probar con `cmd /c openclaw agent --agent <id> --message \"...\"`\n  6. luego aГұadir bindings/routing si hace falta conectarlo a canales\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:/Users/Gustavo/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\",\"content\":\"# MEMORY.md\\n\\n## OperaciГіn / OpenClaw\\n\\n- Para crear nuevos agentes aislados en OpenClaw, existe un playbook replicable en `workspace/agents-setup-playbook.md`.\\n- Caso base ya implementado: **Hestia**.\\n- PatrГіn recordatorio:\\n  1. `cmd /c openclaw agents add <id>`\\n  2. copiar auth desde `main`\\n  3. no configurar canales en el wizard si la ruta aГәn no estГЎ clara\\n  4. personalizar `workspace-<id>/IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md` y `SOUL.md`\\n  5. probar con `cmd /c openclaw agent --agent <id> --message \\\"...\\\"`\\n  6. luego aГұadir bindings/routing si hace falta conectarlo a canales\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":133,"output":245,"cacheRead":