{"type":"message","id":"c1c27782","parentId":"ad0a433b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:01:01.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"La sesiГіn persistente normal por subagent aquГӯ requiere thread, asГӯ que voy a probar invocarla por CLI y obtener su respuesta directa.\n","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c2c34cbd748191b8fbe4476326626a\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qkQBrFTPPND14MiPcppkD9mS|fc_07843e13d03825ba0169c2c34d785c819190a8f33a03de84a9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cmd /c openclaw agent --agent hestia --message \"Hola Hestia. Gustavo te saluda. En una respuesta corta: quien eres y que haces?\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"cmd /c openclaw agent --agent hestia --message \\\"Hola Hestia. Gustavo te saluda. En una respuesta corta: quien eres y que haces?\\\"\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"timeout\":120}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":179,"output":115,"cacheRead":42368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42662,"cost":{"input":0.00044750000000000004,"output":0.001725,"cacheRead":0.010591999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012764499999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774371657659,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c2c34bc33481918200f3ca5ef6e875"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68303c53","parentId":"c1c27782","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:01:10.345Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_qkQBrFTPPND14MiPcppkD9mS|fc_07843e13d03825ba0169c2c34d785c819190a8f33a03de84a9","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hola Gustavo, soy Hestia рҹҸ , tu asistente del hogar; coordino y doy seguimiento a lo de casa con mensajes claros, cortos y Гәtiles."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9025,"aggregated":"Hola Gustavo, soy Hestia рҹҸ , tu asistente del hogar; coordino y doy seguimiento a lo de casa con mensajes claros, cortos y Гәtiles.","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774371670343}}
{"type":"message","id":"c37dcf00","parentId":"68303c53","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:01:17.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Le hablГ© por invocaciГіn directa y esto respondiГі Hestia:\n\nвҖңHola Gustavo, soy Hestia рҹҸ , tu asistente del hogar; coordino y doy seguimiento a lo de casa con mensajes claros, cortos y Гәtiles.вҖқ\n\nO sea: **sГӯ responde**, pero todavГӯa no quedГі como **sesiГіn conversable permanente** dentro de esta interfaz.  \nAhora mismo la puedo consultar por agente, no por chat vivo independiente.\n\nSi quieres, el siguiente paso es dejar a Hestia en una sesiГіn/thread persistente para hablarle directo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c2c35bb91881918f317fd518ed1335\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":41171,"output":122,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42829,"cost":{"input":0.1029275,"output":0.00183,"cacheRead":0.000384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1051415}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774371670345,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c2c35870c0819187acf85949083a40"}}
