{"type":"message","id":"bcbe5d55","parentId":"c196d1b9","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:47:26.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Si Jorge te escribe por WhatsApp, ya deberГӯa caer en Hestia y ella saludarlo desde ese chat.\n\nSi lo que quieres es que **yo provoque un saludo saliente a Jorge ahora mismo**, eso todavГӯa no lo estoy haciendo automГЎticamente desde aquГӯ.  \nLo que sГӯ dirГӯa Hestia es:\n\nHola Jorge, buen dГӯa. Espero que estГ©s muy bien.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c2ce2d77ac8191b1bf1f87ac002028\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":217,"output":85,"cacheRead":61312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61614,"cost":{"input":0.0005425,"output":0.001275,"cacheRead":0.015328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0171455}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774374442102,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c2ce2c68ec81918571b9c5866429c7"}}
