{"type":"message","id":"d5b985ab","parentId":"693a71d4","timestamp":"2026-03-24T20:44:06.698Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Nada todavГӯa sobre el repo de Prometeo.\n\nSolo te dije que iba a revisar:\n- si **Prometeo ya existe**\n- cГіmo conectarlo limpio al repo\n- sin romper el patrГіn de agentes aislados\n\nO sea, **todavГӯa no hice cambios** en:\n- `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\Documents\\tradelab-front`\n- config de Prometeo\n- PRs\n- ramas\n\nSi quieres, ahora sГӯ lo hago.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c2f79721948191a4a7fcecab74d656\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":276,"output":105,"cacheRead":66048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66429,"cost":{"input":0.0006900000000000001,"output":0.001575,"cacheRead":0.016512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018777}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774385041737,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c2f794bedc81919b1084e095a3c419"}}
