{"type":"message","id":"c93ea352","parentId":"d6842924","timestamp":"2026-03-24T20:47:41.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo. Ya quedГі guardado.\n\nPrometeo ahora tiene explГӯcitamente esto:\n\n- **repo:** `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\Documents\\tradelab-front`\n- **rama de trabajo:** `agent-workspace`\n- **destino de PRs:** `main`\n\nLo guardГ© en:\n- `workspace-prometeo/USER.md`\n- `workspace-prometeo/SOUL.md`\n- `workspace/MEMORY.md`\n\nY ademГЎs lo verifiquГ© con una prueba real: Prometeo respondiГі exactamente eso.\n\nSi quieres, lo siguiente es dejarle tambiГ©n el **protocolo operativo de cГіdigo**:\n- actualizar `agent-workspace`\n- trabajar ahГӯ\n- commit limpio\n- PR a `main`  \npara que no improvise despuГ©s.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c2f86c448c8191b78042170b9725d2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":150,"output":168,"cacheRead":70400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70718,"cost":{"input":0.000375,"output":0.00252,"cacheRead":0.017599999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020495}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774385255997,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c2f86b3ae481918f1983f48185c5b3"}}
