{"type":"message","id":"d70a5d1e","parentId":"afefbcbb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:23:08.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_k1cUrqBsoOW2phwj1kCd6tQV|fc_07843e13d03825ba0169c300be591481919cdf0675ba6b3b92","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/Gustavo/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/gog/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":260},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:/Users/Gustavo/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/gog/SKILL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":260}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":242,"output":50,"cacheRead":78720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79012,"cost":{"input":0.0006050000000000001,"output":0.00075,"cacheRead":0.01968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021034999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774387384661,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c300bbf8108191a4092e07f0f23d22"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10d20940","parentId":"d70a5d1e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:23:08.801Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_k1cUrqBsoOW2phwj1kCd6tQV|fc_07843e13d03825ba0169c300be591481919cdf0675ba6b3b92","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gog\ndescription: Google Workspace CLI for Gmail, Calendar, Drive, Contacts, Sheets, and Docs.\nhomepage: https://gogcli.sh\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"рҹҺ®\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"gog\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"steipete/tap/gogcli\",\n              \"bins\": [\"gog\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install gog (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# gog\n\nUse `gog` for Gmail/Calendar/Drive/Contacts/Sheets/Docs. Requires OAuth setup.\n\nSetup (once)\n\n- `gog auth credentials /path/to/client_secret.json`\n- `gog auth add you@gmail.com --services gmail,calendar,drive,contacts,docs,sheets`\n- `gog auth list`\n\nCommon commands\n\n- Gmail search: `gog gmail search 'newer_than:7d' --max 10`\n- Gmail messages search (per email, ignores threading): `gog gmail messages search \"in:inbox from:ryanair.com\" --max 20 --account you@example.com`\n- Gmail send (plain): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body \"Hello\"`\n- Gmail send (multi-line): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-file ./message.txt`\n- Gmail send (stdin): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-file -`\n- Gmail send (HTML): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-html \"<p>Hello</p>\"`\n- Gmail draft: `gog gmail drafts create --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-file ./message.txt`\n- Gmail send draft: `gog gmail drafts send <draftId>`\n- Gmail reply: `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Re: Hi\" --body \"Reply\" --reply-to-message-id <msgId>`\n- Calendar list events: `gog calendar events <calendarId> --from <iso> --to <iso>`\n- Calendar create event: `gog calendar create <calendarId> --summary \"Title\" --from <iso> --to <iso>`\n- Calendar create with color: `gog calendar create <calendarId> --summary \"Title\" --from <iso> --to <iso> --event-color 7`\n- Calendar update event: `gog calendar update <calendarId> <eventId> --summary \"New Title\" --event-color 4`\n- Calendar show colors: `gog calendar colors`\n- Drive search: `gog drive search \"query\" --max 10`\n- Contacts: `gog contacts list --max 20`\n- Sheets get: `gog sheets get <sheetId> \"Tab!A1:D10\" --json`\n- Sheets update: `gog sheets update <sheetId> \"Tab!A1:B2\" --values-json '[[\"A\",\"B\"],[\"1\",\"2\"]]' --input USER_ENTERED`\n- Sheets append: `gog sheets append <sheetId> \"Tab!A:C\" --values-json '[[\"x\",\"y\",\"z\"]]' --insert INSERT_ROWS`\n- Sheets clear: `gog sheets clear <sheetId> \"Tab!A2:Z\"`\n- Sheets metadata: `gog sheets metadata <sheetId> --json`\n- Docs export: `gog docs export <docId> --format txt --out /tmp/doc.txt`\n- Docs cat: `gog docs cat <docId>`\n\nCalendar Colors\n\n- Use `gog calendar colors` to see all available event colors (IDs 1-11)\n- Add colors to events with `--event-color <id>` flag\n- Event color IDs (from `gog calendar colors` output):\n  - 1: #a4bdfc\n  - 2: #7ae7bf\n  - 3: #dbadff\n  - 4: #ff887c\n  - 5: #fbd75b\n  - 6: #ffb878\n  - 7: #46d6db\n  - 8: #e1e1e1\n  - 9: #5484ed\n  - 10: #51b749\n  - 11: #dc2127\n\nEmail Formatting\n\n- Prefer plain text. Use `--body-file` for multi-paragraph messages (or `--body-file -` for stdin).\n- Same `--body-file` pattern works for drafts and replies.\n- `--body` does not unescape `\\n`. If you need inline newlines, use a heredoc or `$'Line 1\\n\\nLine 2'`.\n- Use `--body-html` only when you need rich formatting.\n- HTML tags: `<p>` for paragraphs, `<br>` for line breaks, `<strong>` for bold, `<em>` for italic, `<a href=\"url\">` for links, `<ul>`/`<li>` for lists.\n- Example (plain text via stdin):\n\n  ```bash\n  gog gmail send --to recipient@example.com \\\n    --subject \"Meeting Follow-up\" \\\n    --body-file - <<'EOF'\n  Hi Name,\n\n  Thanks for meeting today. Next steps:\n  - Item one\n  - Item two\n\n  Best regards,\n  Your Name\n  EOF\n  ```\n\n- Example (HTML list):\n  ```bash\n  gog gmail send --to recipient@example.com \\\n    --subject \"Meeting Follow-up\" \\\n    --body-html \"<p>Hi Name,</p><p>Thanks for meeting today. Here are the next steps:</p><ul><li>Item one</li><li>Item two</li></ul><p>Best regards,<br>Your Name</p>\"\n  ```\n\nNotes\n\n- Set `GOG_ACCOUNT=you@gmail.com` to avoid repeating `--account`.\n- For scripting, prefer `--json` plus `--no-input`.\n- Sheets values can be passed via `--values-json` (recommended) or as inline rows.\n- Docs supports export/cat/copy. In-place edits require a Docs API client (not in gog).\n- Confirm before sending mail or creating events.\n- `gog gmail search` returns one row per thread; use `gog gmail messages search` when you need every individual email returned separately.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774387388798}}
{"type":"message","id":"f80b22c5","parentId":"10d20940","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:23:22.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No hay skill de Notion ni herramienta directa para Notion aquГӯ. No voy a inventar una integraciГіn. Lo correcto es decГӯrtelo claro y darte el esquema listo para copiar, o pedir un mecanismo concreto si quieres que lo ejecute.\n","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c300c24e48819191b7de2aace7f0fa\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No pude proceder de verdad sobre **Notion** desde aquГӯ porque **en esta instalaciГіn no tengo herramienta/integraciГіn de Notion**.\n\nO sea, no te voy a vender humo:\n- **permiso sГӯ me diste**\n- **capacidad directa a Notion en esta sesiГіn:** no la tengo\n\n## Lo que sГӯ puedo hacer ahora mismo\nDejarte el **contenido exacto, visual y listo para montar** en `Atlas OS`, para que lo pegues o para usar una integraciГіn cuando la tengas.\n\n## Te propongo esto para Atlas OS\n\n### Estados\n- рҹ“Ҙ Inbox\n- рҹ§© Definir\n- в–¶пёҸ Listo\n- вҡҷпёҸ En progreso\n- вҸёпёҸ En espera\n- рҹҡ§ Bloqueado\n- вң… Hecho\n\n### Agentes\n- вҡЎ Atlas\n- рҹҸ  Hestia\n- рҹ”Ҙ Prometeo\n- вҡ”пёҸ Ares\n\n### Prioridad\n- рҹ”ҙ Alta\n- рҹҹЎ Media\n- рҹҹў Baja\n\n### Tipos\n- рҹӣ пёҸ Task\n- рҹҗһ Bug\n- рҹ’Ў Idea\n- рҹ“Ң Seguimiento\n- рҹ§ұ Proyecto\n- рҹ§  DecisiГіn\n\n## Propiedades de la base de datos\n- **Nombre**\n- **Estado**\n- **Agente**\n- **Prioridad**\n- **Tipo**\n- **Proyecto**\n- **Siguiente acciГіn**\n- **Bloqueado por**\n- **Fecha**\n- **Notas**\n- **Origen**\n- **Activo**\n\n## Vistas\n- **Tablero principal** вҶ’ por Estado\n- **Por agente** вҶ’ agrupado por Agente\n- **Hoy** вҶ’ prioridad alta + activas\n- **Bloqueados**\n- **Hecho reciente**\n- **Inbox rГЎpido**\n\n## CГіmo usarlo conmigo\n- tГә pones ideas o pendientes en **Inbox**\n- yo los aterrizo y los paso a **Definir** o **Listo**\n- cuando estemos trabajando algo, lo marco en **вҡҷпёҸ En progreso**\n- si se traba, **рҹҡ§ Bloqueado**\n- cuando sale, **вң… Hecho**\n\n## Si quieres que lo haga yo de verdad\nNecesito una de estas:\n1. una **integraciГіn real de Notion** disponible aquГӯ, o\n2. que me compartas el contenido/export y yo te devuelvo el tablero estructurado listo para pegar\n\n## Lo honesto en una lГӯnea\n**No modifiquГ© Notion porque aquГӯ no tengo acceso directo a Notion.**  \nPero sГӯ te puedo dejar **el tablero exacto** listo para montar ya.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c300c352008191b63c4f39a5397bf5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1567,"output":612,"cacheRead":78848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81027,"cost":{"input":0.0039175,"output":0.00918,"cacheRead":0.019712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032809500000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774387388802,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c300c006b481919b75ce58a1bcb45a"}}
