{"type":"message","id":"d4960920","parentId":"4e526246","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:24:30.867Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No. **En esta sesiГіn no tengo acceso operativo a Notion**.\n\nSi lo tuviera, ya habrГӯa hecho una acciГіn real y te lo dirГӯa claro.  \nLo que sГӯ tengo aquГӯ es acceso a:\n- archivos\n- shell\n- web\n- sesiones\n- memoria\n- cron\n\nPero **no veo herramienta/integraciГіn de Notion** disponible.\n\nSi quieres, puedo revisar contigo si en tu mГЎquina ya existe alguna integraciГіn local para Notion y, si existe, la uso yo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3010f237c8191b6f85f798d6f5c85\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":204,"output":111,"cacheRead":81280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81595,"cost":{"input":0.00051,"output":0.001665,"cacheRead":0.020319999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022494999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774387464165,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3010bcb388191b89a5b86c718def8"}}
