{"type":"message","id":"83f6ebc6","parentId":"823ae038","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:24:53.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c301264a588191a10dd8313b11642b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Entonces lo correcto es **revisar cuГЎl acceso a Notion hay en la mГЎquina** y usar ese.\n\nVoy a buscar si tienes:\n- Notion CLI\n- MCP de Notion\n- scripts\n- integraciones locales configuradas\n\ny si existe algo usable, lo opero yo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30126651481918b079b3419584092\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":272,"output":76,"cacheRead":81408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81756,"cost":{"input":0.00068,"output":0.00114,"cacheRead":0.020352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022171999999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774387488880,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c301241378819192bc303499d50cc6"}}
