{"type":"message","id":"c877e0eb","parentId":"a674503a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:34:38.553Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo.\n\nYa dejГ© esto **guardado en memoria**:\n- que **sГӯ tenemos integraciГіn con Notion**\n- que **Atlas OS** serГЎ tablero operativo vivo\n- que debo **revisarlo todos los dГӯas a las 8:00 AM**\n- y coordinar desde ahГӯ con subagentes cuando haga sentido\n\nAdemГЎs, ya te lo **programГ©**:\n\n- **Job:** `daily-atlas-os-review`\n- **Hora:** `8:00 AM`\n- **Zona:** `America/Bogota`\n\nID del cron:\n- `03b29602-b584-4ec0-9241-b0d74393cc82`\n\nY quedГі **commiteado** en memoria.\n\nEn corto: **sГӯ, ya quedГі recordado y automatizado**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3036dcc2881919e7b414d9088f966\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":171,"output":169,"cacheRead":94848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95188,"cost":{"input":0.00042750000000000004,"output":0.002535,"cacheRead":0.023712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0266745}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388071825,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3036b2b0c8191b465d80a34a3d4c1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f3e72c2","parentId":"c877e0eb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:35:51.774Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:34:34 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:34:37 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:35:37 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:35:41 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:35 GMT-5] quiero que apenas se encienta el pc se lance el comando openclaw gateway start como lo hao ?"}],"timestamp":1774388151770}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5cf4441","parentId":"8f3e72c2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:36:03.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] En Windows, hazlo con **Task Scheduler**.  \nLa idea es: **al iniciar el PC** вҶ’ correr `openclaw gateway start`.\n\n## OpciГіn recomendada: Programador de tareas\n\n### 1. Abre Task Scheduler\n- `Win + R`\n- escribe: `taskschd.msc`\n\n### 2. Crea una tarea\n- **Create Task**  \n  no вҖңBasic TaskвҖқ, mejor la completa\n\n### 3. PestaГұa **General**\n- **Name:** `OpenClaw Gateway Start`\n- marca:\n  - **Run whether user is logged on or not**\n  - **Run with highest privileges**\n\n### 4. PestaГұa **Triggers**\n- **New**\n- **Begin the task:** `At startup`\n\n### 5. PestaГұa **Actions**\n- **New**\n- **Action:** `Start a program`\n\nPon esto:\n\n- **Program/script:**  \n  `cmd.exe`\n\n- **Add arguments:**  \n  `/c openclaw gateway start`\n\n### 6. PestaГұa **Conditions**\n- desmarca restricciones innecesarias tipo energГӯa si quieres que siempre arranque\n\n### 7. PestaГұa **Settings**\n- marca:\n  - **Allow task to be run on demand**\n  - **Run task as soon as possible after a scheduled start is missed**\n  - **If the task fails, restart every:** 1 minute\n  - intenta 3 veces\n\n---\n\n## Mejor aГәn: usar ruta absoluta\nPara evitar problemas de PATH, primero revisa dГіnde estГЎ `openclaw`.\n\nEn PowerShell:\n```powershell\nwhere.exe openclaw\n```\n\nSeguramente serГЎ algo como:\n```text\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd\n```\n\nSi sale eso, mejor usa:\n\n- **Program/script:**  \n  `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd`\n\n- **Add arguments:**  \n  `gateway start`\n\nEso es mГЎs robusto.\n\n---\n\n## CГіmo probar\nDespuГ©s de crearla:\n\n- en Task Scheduler\n- clic derecho sobre la tarea\n- **Run**\n\nLuego verifica:\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n---\n\n## Si quieres, yo te la puedo crear\nPuedo dejГЎrtela creada desde aquГӯ con `schtasks`, pero eso ya es tocar arranque del sistema.  \nSi quieres que lo haga yo, dime:\n\n**вҖңsГӯ, crГ©ala tГәвҖқ**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c303bcc2648191a43c7cc4b20aabdb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1229,"output":527,"cacheRead":95360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97116,"cost":{"input":0.0030725,"output":0.007905,"cacheRead":0.02384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0348175}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388151775,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c303bb19988191ad2be3ed0e9b7cc6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff04cc45","parentId":"a5cf4441","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:40:30.699Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:36:41 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:36:45 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:37:45 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:37:50 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:38:50 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:38:53 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:39:53 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:39:57 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:40 GMT-5] al darle ok me pide user y contrasena pero yo no tengo contrasena puesta"}],"timestamp":1774388430693}}
{"type":"message","id":"db357574","parentId":"ff04cc45","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:40:41.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, eso pasa por esta opciГіn:\n\n- **Run whether user is logged on or not**\n\nCuando marcas eso, Windows te pide credenciales de la cuenta.\n\n## Si no tienes contraseГұa\nTienes dos caminos:\n\n### OpciГіn simple\nUsa:\n- **Run only when user is logged on**\n\nAsГӯ **no te pedirГЎ contraseГұa**.\n\nY deja marcado:\n- **Run with highest privileges**\n\nPara tu caso, probablemente **esto basta** si el PC lo usas tГә y OpenClaw debe arrancar cuando inicias sesiГіn.\n\n---\n\n## CГіmo dejarlo entonces\n### General\n- **Name:** `OpenClaw Gateway Start`\n- selecciona:\n  - **Run only when user is logged on**\n  - **Run with highest privileges**\n\n### Trigger\n- **At log on**  \n  mejor que вҖңAt startupвҖқ si no tienes contraseГұa configurada\n\n### Action\nSi `where openclaw` te da algo como esto:\n```text\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd\n```\n\npon:\n\n- **Program/script:**  \n  `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd`\n\n- **Add arguments:**  \n  `gateway start`\n\n---\n\n## RecomendaciГіn real para ti\nComo no tienes contraseГұa:\n- **no uses** вҖңRun whether user is logged on or notвҖқ\n- usa **At log on**\n- con **Run only when user is logged on**\n\nEs lo mГЎs fГЎcil y funcional.\n\nSi quieres, te digo exactamente quГ© llenar campo por campo segГәn tu PC.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c304d600288191a7ee6815012a1864\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1122,"output":337,"cacheRead":95104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96563,"cost":{"input":0.002805,"output":0.0050550000000000005,"cacheRead":0.023776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031636}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388430700,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c304d2cb448191b83befa7e6514ce5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4f06526","parentId":"db357574","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:41:34.650Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:40:57 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:41:01 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:41 GMT-5] es que quiero que se innnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnncie sesion solo y ejecute eso ya que no estoy pendiente ya programe el encesdiod desde la bios"}],"timestamp":1774388494646}}
{"type":"message","id":"03a341d4","parentId":"d4f06526","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:41:47.349Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Entonces necesitas **auto-login de Windows** + tarea al iniciar sesiГіn.\n\nPorque sin contraseГұa, Windows no puede ejecutar una tarea вҖңcomo usuarioвҖқ en segundo plano antes del login de forma limpia.  \nLa forma prГЎctica para tu caso es:\n\n## Lo que quieres realmente\n1. el PC se enciende solo desde BIOS  \n2. Windows **inicia sesiГіn automГЎticamente**\n3. al entrar, corre:\n   - `openclaw gateway start`\n\n## CГіmo hacerlo\n\n### Paso 1: activar auto-login\nHaz esto:\n\n- `Win + R`\n- escribe:\n  ```text\n  netplwiz\n  ```\n\nSe abre la ventana de cuentas.\n\nAhГӯ:\n- selecciona tu usuario\n- desmarca:\n  - **Users must enter a user name and password to use this computer**\n    o en espaГұol algo como:\n  - **Los usuarios deben escribir su nombre y contraseГұa para usar el equipo**\n\nLe das Apply.\n\n### Si no tienes contraseГұa\nA veces te deja poner los campos vacГӯos.  \nSi no, te recomiendo poner una contraseГұa simple local y usarla solo para el auto-login.\n\n---\n\n## Paso 2: crear la tarea\nEn Task Scheduler:\n\n### General\n- **Run only when user is logged on**\n- **Run with highest privileges**\n\n### Trigger\n- **At log on**\n\n### Action\nUsa mejor ruta absoluta.\n\nPrimero averigua:\n```powershell\nwhere.exe openclaw\n```\n\nLuego pon eso como:\n- **Program/script**\n\nY en argumentos:\n```text\ngateway start\n```\n\n---\n\n## Resultado\nEntonces quedarГЎ asГӯ:\n\n- BIOS prende el PC\n- Windows entra solo\n- OpenClaw gateway arranca solo\n\n## Si quieres algo todavГӯa mГЎs simple\nEn vez de Task Scheduler, puedes meter un `.bat` en la carpeta **Startup** de Windows.\n\nPor ejemplo crear:\n\n```bat\n@echo off\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\nen:\n```text\nshell:startup\n```\n\nPero yo prefiero **Task Scheduler**, porque es mГЎs estable.\n\n---\n\n## RecomendaciГіn honesta\nPara tu caso:\n- **auto-login + Task Scheduler al logon**\nes la soluciГіn correcta.\n\nSi quieres, te doy el paso a paso exacto con:\n- auto-login\n- tarea\n- script `.bat`\ntodo listo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c305150a58819184e45589da527ff0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":349,"output":483,"cacheRead":96384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97216,"cost":{"input":0.0008725000000000001,"output":0.007245000000000001,"cacheRead":0.024096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0322135}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388494650,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3051254e48191a776d86c612d40de"}}
{"type":"message","id":"75a8faeb","parentId":"03a341d4","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:44:16.993Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:42:01 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:42:04 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:43:04 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:43:08 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:44:08 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:44:11 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:44 GMT-5] no quiero colcoarle contrasena"}],"timestamp":1774388656989}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e4ab5d4","parentId":"75a8faeb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:44:27.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Entonces te toca la ruta sin contraseГұa:\n\n## SГӯ se puede, pero asГӯ:\n- **auto-login sin contraseГұa**\n- y luego **ejecutar OpenClaw al iniciar sesiГіn**\n\n## Prueba primero esto\n### 1. `netplwiz`\n- `Win + R`\n- escribe:\n  ```text\n  netplwiz\n  ```\n- si te deja desmarcar:\n  - **Los usuarios deben escribir su nombre y contraseГұa para usar el equipo**\n- Apply / OK\n\nEn algunas instalaciones de Windows, con cuenta local y sin contraseГұa, eso puede bastar.\n\n---\n\n## Si `netplwiz` no te deja o no funciona\nHazlo por **Startup folder**, mГЎs simple que Task Scheduler en tu caso.\n\n### Paso 1\nAbre:\n- `Win + R`\n- escribe:\n  ```text\n  shell:startup\n  ```\n\n### Paso 2\nCrea un archivo `.bat`, por ejemplo:\n\n`openclaw-start.bat`\n\ncon esto:\n```bat\n@echo off\nstart \"\" \"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd\" gateway start\n```\n\n### Paso 3\nGuГЎrdalo ahГӯ.\n\n---\n\n## QuГ© hace esto\nCuando Windows entre automГЎticamente a tu escritorio:\n- abre ese script\n- lanza:\n  - `openclaw gateway start`\n\n## Entonces el flujo serГӯa\n- BIOS enciende PC\n- Windows entra solo\n- carpeta Startup corre el `.bat`\n- OpenClaw gateway arranca\n\n---\n\n## Lo importante\nSin contraseГұa, **no te recomiendo pelear con Task Scheduler en modo oculto/sistema**.  \nLa opciГіn mГЎs simple y estable para ti es:\n\n- **auto-login**\n- **Startup folder + .bat**\n\n## Si quieres, yo te preparo el `.bat`\ny te digo exactamente dГіnde ponerlo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c305b6e0708191a8aa924e80971ae5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":436,"output":394,"cacheRead":97024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97854,"cost":{"input":0.00109,"output":0.00591,"cacheRead