{"type":"message","id":"7665fa7c","parentId":"89f33f22","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:46:30.867Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, **eso te sirve bastante bien**.\n\nEse script ya estГЎ pensado para lanzar el gateway minimizado:\n\n```bat\n@echo off\nrem OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.23-1)\nstart \"\" /min cmd.exe /d /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\n```\n\n## QuГ© harГӯa yo\nUsar **ese mismo** en el arranque.\n\n## OpciГіn simple\nPon un acceso o un `.bat` que lo invoque en:\n\n```text\nshell:startup\n```\n\n## Incluso puedes usarlo directo\nSi el archivo existe en:\n\n```text\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\n```\n\nentonces crea en la carpeta Startup un `.bat` asГӯ:\n\n```bat\n@echo off\nstart \"\" /min cmd.exe /d /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\n```\n\n## Mejor que `openclaw gateway start`?\nPara tu caso, **sГӯ**.  \nPorque ya usa la ruta/local wrapper que OpenClaw dejГі preparado.\n\n## En corto\n- **sГӯ existe**\n- **sГӯ sirve**\n- **sГӯ lo usarГӯa para el autoarranque**\n\nSi quieres, el siguiente paso es solo:\n- meterlo en **Startup**\ny listo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c306324c70819190f993484c8cebaf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":369,"output":285,"cacheRead":97664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98318,"cost":{"input":0.0009225,"output":0.004275,"cacheRead":0.024416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0296135}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388773976,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3062a22b08191a281e57510dc90d8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdb9e3c6","parentId":"7665fa7c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:47:01.233Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:46:15 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:46:19 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:47 GMT-5] osea si esta aca C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Start Menu\\Programs\\Startup el lo ejecuta al inciar ?"}],"timestamp":1774388821228}}
{"type":"message","id":"9aa24519","parentId":"fdb9e3c6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:47:08.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ.\n\nSi ese `.bat` o acceso directo estГЎ en:\n\n- `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Start Menu\\Programs\\Startup`\n\nWindows lo ejecuta **cuando inicia tu sesiГіn**.\n\n## Ojo con la precisiГіn\nNo es exactamente:\n- вҖңcuando prende el PCвҖқ\n\nSino:\n- **cuando Windows entra a tu usuario**\n\nEntonces, si ademГЎs logras:\n- encendido por BIOS\n- **auto-login**\n\nel efecto prГЎctico serГЎ el que quieres:\n- prende el PC\n- entra solo\n- ejecuta ese script\n- arranca OpenClaw\n\n## En corto\n**SГӯ, si estГЎ ahГӯ, se ejecuta al iniciar sesiГіn.**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3065bbde88191a1dee51f4a52dcaf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":310,"output":156,"cacheRead":98176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98642,"cost":{"input":0.0007750000000000001,"output":0.00234,"cacheRead":0.024544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027659}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388821233,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c306592f5c8191811a7a83d4d4615a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b322415a","parentId":"9aa24519","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:47:54.050Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:47:04 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:47:09 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:47 GMT-5] el autttttttttttttttttt login se puede configuarar"}],"timestamp":1774388874043}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5b5b6d1","parentId":"b322415a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:48:05.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, **se puede configurar**.\n\nLa forma clГЎsica en Windows es:\n\n## MГ©todo 1 вҖ” `netplwiz`\n1. `Win + R`\n2. escribe:\n   ```text\n   netplwiz\n   ```\n3. selecciona tu usuario\n4. desmarca:\n   - **Los usuarios deben escribir su nombre y contraseГұa para usar el equipo**\n5. Apply / OK\n\n## Pero ojo en tu caso\nSi **no tienes contraseГұa**, puede pasar una de estas:\n- funcione igual\n- no te deje quitarlo\n- o Windows ni muestre esa opciГіn dependiendo de la configuraciГіn\n\n---\n\n## MГ©todo 2 вҖ” ConfiguraciГіn/registro\nTambiГ©n se puede forzar con configuraciГіn del sistema/registro, **pero ahГӯ ya estГЎs tocando login automГЎtico de Windows**, y prefiero no ponerte a editar eso a ciegas en un mensaje corto.\n\n## Lo prГЎctico\nPrimero prueba **`netplwiz`**.  \nSi te deja, ya estГЎ.\n\n## Si no te deja\nEntonces te digo el siguiente mГ©todo correcto segГәn:\n- si tu cuenta es **local**\no\n- si es **Microsoft account**\n\nPorque cambia un poco.\n\nEn corto:\n**sГӯ, se puede.**  \nPrueba `netplwiz` primero.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30692a5cc8191b45f02024e8ddf2c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":56285,"output":267,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99048,"cost":{"input":0.14071250000000002,"output":0.004005,"cacheRead":0.010624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15534150000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388874050,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3068d7534819183b32f83c1d00e0a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e661fba","parentId":"d5b5b6d1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:49:36.688Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:48:09 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:48:12 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:49:12 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:49:16 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:49 GMT-5] entre local users and groups"}],"timestamp":1774388976683}}
{"type":"message","id":"0cad46dc","parentId":"0e661fba","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:49:43.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No, **no es ahГӯ**.\n\n`Local Users and Groups` sirve mГЎs para administrar cuentas y grupos del sistema, **no es la vГӯa normal para auto-login**.\n\n## Lo que debes abrir es:\n- `Win + R`\n- escribe:\n  ```text\n  netplwiz\n  ```\n\no tambiГ©n:\n```text\ncontrol userpasswords2\n```\n\nEso abre la ventana correcta para configurar el inicio de sesiГіn automГЎtico.\n\n## En corto\n- **Local Users and Groups:** no\n- **netplwiz:** sГӯ","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c306f816608191868d5931152f5e34\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":55286,"output":119,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97901,"cost":{"input":0.138215,"output":0.0017850000000000001,"cacheRead":0.010624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.150624}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774388976688,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c306f42b448191b2218b08fcff96f1"}}
