{"type":"message","id":"a36248fb","parentId":"e9fe13b7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:50:37.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, porque sigues en la ventana equivocada.\n\nEso que describes es de **Local Users and Groups**.\n\n## Sal de ahГӯ y abre esto:\n1. `Win + R`\n2. escribe exactamente:\n   ```text\n   netplwiz\n   ```\n3. Enter\n\n## La ventana correcta debe mostrar:\n- una lista de usuarios\n- y arriba o abajo una casilla tipo:\n  - **Users must enter a user name and password to use this computer**\n  - o en espaГұol equivalente\n\nSi no ves esa casilla, me dices y te guГӯo con el siguiente mГ©todo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3072d133c8191b46d143460c7847a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":253,"output":131,"cacheRead":97792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98176,"cost":{"input":0.0006325,"output":0.001965,"cacheRead":0.024447999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027045499999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389030066,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30729e43c8191b61398c4bea1acb4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0c1ebda","parentId":"a36248fb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:51:27.918Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:51:20 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:51:24 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:51 GMT-5] no me aparece eso"}],"timestamp":1774389087914}}
{"type":"message","id":"c8b1630b","parentId":"b0c1ebda","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:51:39.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, pasa en Windows 11 en algunos equipos.  \nCuando **no aparece esa casilla en `netplwiz`**, normalmente es porque estГЎ activo el requisito de **Windows Hello** para cuentas Microsoft/local.\n\nHaz esto:\n\n## Paso 1\nAbre:\n\n- **ConfiguraciГіn**\n- **Cuentas**\n- **Opciones de inicio de sesiГіn**\n\n## Paso 2\nBusca una opciГіn parecida a:\n\n- **For improved security, only allow Windows Hello sign-in for Microsoft accounts on this device**\n- o en espaГұol algo como:\n- **Para mayor seguridad, permitir solo el inicio de sesiГіn con Windows Hello...**\n\n## Paso 3\n**DesactГӯvala**\n\n## Paso 4\nVuelve a abrir:\n```text\nnetplwiz\n```\n\nY ahГӯ ya deberГӯa aparecer la casilla de:\n- **Los usuarios deben escribir su nombre y contraseГұa para usar el equipo**\n\n---\n\n## Pero ojo\nSi realmente **no tienes contraseГұa**, aun quitando eso puede seguir habiendo limitaciones raras.\n\n## Si no aparece ni asГӯ\nEntonces ya toca el mГ©todo alterno por **registro/autologon**.\n\nSi quieres, te guГӯo paso a paso con eso tambiГ©n.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3076987948191afa427f5dd126a33\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":264,"output":252,"cacheRead":98048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98564,"cost":{"input":0.0006600000000000001,"output":0.00378,"cacheRead":0.024512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028952}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389087918,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30765434881919735f2a11bd90a72"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c2d5b84","parentId":"c8b1630b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:52:17.813Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:52 GMT-5] aca Control Panel\\User Accounts\\User Accounts ?"}],"timestamp":1774389137809}}
{"type":"message","id":"a189110d","parentId":"9c2d5b84","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:52:23.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No exactamente.\n\nLa ruta Гәtil no es entrar navegando por `User Accounts` normal, sino abrir directamente:\n\n- `Win + R`\n- escribe:\n  ```text\n  netplwiz\n  ```\n\n## Pero antes\nVe aquГӯ:\n\n- **Settings**\n- **Accounts**\n- **Sign-in options**\n\ny desactiva la opciГіn de **Windows Hello only** / **solo permitir Windows Hello** si aparece.\n\nDespuГ©s sГӯ:\n- `Win + R`\n- `netplwiz`\n\n## En corto\n- `Control Panel > User Accounts > User Accounts`: no es la ruta buena\n- `Settings > Accounts > Sign-in options`: sГӯ\n- `netplwiz`: sГӯ","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3079721708191a911f022b435834c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":220,"output":150,"cacheRead":98432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98802,"cost":{"input":0.00055,"output":0.0022500000000000003,"cacheRead":0.024607999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027408}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389137814,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3079584f481919ff789a1980f581c"}}
