{"type":"message","id":"90c30642","parentId":"39a90f4c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:53:54.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Dale por teclado, mГЎs fГЎcil.\n\n## Haz esto:\n1. Presiona **Win + I**\n   - eso abre **Settings / ConfiguraciГіn**\n\n## Luego entra a:\n- **Accounts**\n- **Sign-in options**\n\ny busca la opciГіn de **Windows Hello only** / **solo Windows Hello**.\n\nSi no la ves o prefieres mГЎs directo, usa esto:\n\n## OpciГіn directa\n1. Presiona **Win + R**\n2. escribe:\n   ```text\n   ms-settings:signinoptions\n   ```\n3. Enter\n\nEso te debe abrir directo a **Sign-in options**.\n\nSi abre, ahГӯ te digo exactamente quГ© buscar.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c307f25a208191b4138630b44921b3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":301,"output":141,"cacheRead":98688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99130,"cost":{"input":0.0007525,"output":0.002115,"cacheRead":0.024672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0275395}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389228448,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c307efe7988191a5ac7857720e9b7c"}}
