{"type":"message","id":"d87b8c3f","parentId":"a9d5ab85","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:55:07.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Vas bien. EstГЎs en el lugar correcto.\n\nAhora busca un switch/opciГіn que diga algo parecido a:\n\n- **For improved security, only allow Windows Hello sign-in for Microsoft accounts on this device**\n- o en espaГұol:\n- **Para mayor seguridad, permitir solo el inicio de sesiГіn de Windows Hello...**\n\nA veces estГЎ mГЎs abajo en esa misma pantalla.\n\n## Si la encuentras\n- **desactГӯvala**\n- luego vuelve a correr:\n  ```text\n  netplwiz\n  ```\n\n## Si no la encuentras\nEntonces ya no vale perder tiempo ahГӯ y toca el mГ©todo alterno.\n\nDime solo una de estas:\n- **вҖңsГӯ la viвҖқ**\n- **вҖңno la veoвҖқ**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3083b728c8191aae92a8cc7c4041b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":324,"output":157,"cacheRead":98944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99425,"cost":{"input":0.0008100000000000001,"output":0.002355,"cacheRead":0.024735999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027901}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389302376,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30839d7088191ae61660039e9280a"}}
