{"type":"message","id":"547ec383","parentId":"55990361","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:56:53.262Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Entonces toca el mГ©todo alterno.\n\n## Ojo importante\n**Sin contraseГұa, auto-login real de Windows es problemГЎtico/no estГЎndar.**  \nLo mГЎs estable normalmente requiere que la cuenta tenga contraseГұa, aunque sea simple.\n\nComo tГә **no quieres poner contraseГұa**, te dirГӯa esto honestamente:\n\n## Lo mГЎs prГЎctico para ti\nNo te mates con auto-login avanzado ahora.  \nHaz primero que:\n\n- el PC encienda solo\n- y si ya quedГі la sesiГіn abierta/no bloqueada, arranque OpenClaw desde Startup\n\n## Pero si quieres insistir con auto-login\nHay dos rutas:\n1. **registro / AutoAdminLogon**\n2. **Sysinternals Autologon**\n\n### La recomendada\n**Autologon de Sysinternals**  \nporque evita editar registro a mano.\n\nPero incluso esa herramienta normalmente espera credenciales de una cuenta.\n\n---\n\n## ConclusiГіn honesta\nSi tu cuenta:\n- **no tiene contraseГұa**\n- y `netplwiz` no muestra la opciГіn\n\nentonces estГЎs en un caso donde **forzar auto-login puede volverse mГЎs fastidioso que Гәtil**.\n\n## Mi recomendaciГіn real\nEl camino limpio serГӯa:\n- poner una contraseГұa simple local\n- activar auto-login\n- Startup con gateway\n\n## Pero como no quieres contraseГұa\nMi siguiente recomendaciГіn serГӯa:\n- revisar si tu PC realmente **se queda en sesiГіn iniciada** tras reinicios/encendidos\n- y usar **Startup** para OpenClaw\n\nSi quieres, te guГӯo por el mГ©todo de **Autologon de Sysinternals** igualmente.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c308a17524819182040b9f5de46690\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":232,"output":332,"cacheRead":99328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99892,"cost":{"input":0.00058,"output":0.00498,"cacheRead":0.024832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030392}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389398391,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30899fdb8819196be9c8fce34f9c6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"be8eab14","parentId":"547ec383","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:57:31.472Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:56:39 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:56:43 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:57 GMT-5] lo que quiero es que se ejecute openclaw al encernder el pc"}],"timestamp":1774389451467}}
{"type":"message","id":"14474853","parentId":"be8eab14","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:57:41.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Entonces quГ©date con esto, simple:\n\n## Si quieres que OpenClaw se ejecute al encender el PC\nnecesitas que ocurra una de estas dos cosas:\n\n### OpciГіn A вҖ” la fГЎcil\n- el PC se enciende\n- Windows entra a tu sesiГіn\n- carpeta **Startup** ejecuta el script\n\n### OpciГіn B вҖ” la avanzada\n- se ejecuta como tarea de sistema antes del login\n\n## Para ti, la buena es la A\nYa tienes prГЎcticamente la pieza correcta:\n\n```bat\n@echo off\nstart \"\" /min cmd.exe /d /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\n```\n\nSi ese script estГЎ en:\n- `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Start Menu\\Programs\\Startup`\n\nentonces **OpenClaw se ejecutarГЎ al iniciar sesiГіn**.\n\n---\n\n## Lo clave\nSi el equipo:\n- prende desde BIOS\n- y entra directo al escritorio\n\nentonces **ya quedaste**.\n\nSi el equipo:\n- prende\n- pero se queda en pantalla de login\n\nentonces **no se va a ejecutar todavГӯa**, porque Startup corre **despuГ©s del login**.\n\n---\n\n## En una lГӯnea\n**Para que OpenClaw arranque al prender el PC, necesitas que Windows tambiГ©n entre a la sesiГіn automГЎticamente.**\n\nSin eso, no hay magia con Startup.\n\n## Respuesta brutalmente prГЎctica\n- **si autoentra a Windows:** sГӯ, ya lo tienes resuelto con Startup\n- **si no autoentra:** no arrancarГЎ solo todavГӯa\n\nSi quieres, te ayudo a comprobar cuГЎl de esos dos comportamientos tiene tu PC.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c308d1fa24819197949f906147549c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":328,"output":355,"cacheRead":99712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100395,"cost":{"input":0.0008200000000000001,"output":0.005325,"cacheRead":0.024928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031073}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389451472,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c308cee7208191be1a16c2a1f8cf24"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a415c27","parentId":"14474853","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:58:07.117Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:57:43 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:57:47 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:58 GMT-5] ### OpciГіn B вҖ” la avanzada\n\n - se ejecuta como tarea de sistema antes del login esta me gustaria"}],"timestamp":1774389487111}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba908230","parentId":"8a415c27","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:58:18.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, esa es la vГӯa para evitar depender del login.\n\nPero aquГӯ hay una diferencia importante:\n\n## Lo que quieres\nEjecutar algo **antes del login**.\n\n## Lo que eso implica\nLa tarea debe correr como:\n- **SYSTEM**\no\n- una cuenta con credenciales guardadas\n\n## Problema con tu caso\nComo no quieres contraseГұa, lo mГЎs viable para **antes del login** es usar:\n\n- **Task Scheduler**\n- cuenta: **SYSTEM**\n- trigger: **At startup**\n\n## Pero ojo\nNo todos los comandos de usuario funcionan igual bajo SYSTEM.  \nEntonces lo correcto es no lanzar algo ambiguo, sino probar el wrapper real:\n\n- `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd`\n\no\n- `openclaw gateway start`\n\n## La forma correcta serГӯa algo como\nCrear una tarea con:\n\n- **Run whether user is logged on or not**\n- **User:** `SYSTEM`\n- **Trigger:** `At startup`\n\nY acciГіn:\n```text\ncmd.exe /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\n```\n\n## Mi advertencia honesta\nPuede fallar si ese script depende de:\n- perfil del usuario\n- PATH de usuario\n- variables de entorno del usuario\n- sesiГіn interactiva\n\n## RecomendaciГіn\nSi quieres esta ruta avanzada, hazla **como prueba**, no como dogma:\n1. crear tarea con SYSTEM\n2. reiniciar\n3. verificar si el gateway quedГі arriba\n\n## Si quieres, yo te dejo el comando exacto\npara crear la tarea con `schtasks`.\n\nSolo dime:\n- **вҖңsГӯ, dame el comando exactoвҖқ**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c308f67354819188d5bb3bf7912073\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":52288,"output":354,"cacheRead":46592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99234,"cost":{"input":0.13072,"output":0.0053100000000000005,"cacheRead":0.011647999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.147678}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389487117,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c308f2cecc8191bde315b97415075e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"029abaf7","parentId":"ba908230","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:59:00.454Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:58:47 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:58:50 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:58 GMT-5] dame el comenado"}],"timestamp":1774389540450}}
{"type":"message","id":"965cae13","parentId":"029abaf7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:59:08.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Usa este en **CMD como administrador**:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"cmd.exe /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\" /F\n```\n\n## QuГ© hace\n- crea una tarea llamada **OpenClaw Gateway Startup**\n- corre **al encender**\n- como **SYSTEM**\n- con privilegios altos\n- ejecuta:\n  - `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd`\n\n## Para probarla sin reiniciar\n```bat\nschtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\"\n```\n\n## Para revisar que exista\n```bat\nschtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /V /FO LIST\n```\n\n## Si quieres borrarla luego\n```bat\nschtasks /Delete /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /F\n```\n\n## Ojo\nSi el script depende de algo de tu perfil de usuario, puede que bajo **SYSTEM** no arranque fino.  \nPero **este es el comando correcto para probar la opciГіn avanzada**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c3092a3ac081918819524a6b6206e6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":298,"output":255,"cacheRead":99072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99625,"cost":{"input":0.0007450000000000001,"output":0.0038250000000000003,"cacheRead":0.024768,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029338}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389540454,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c3092803588191ba8515fd196d7516"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b1fa5a2","parentId":"965cae13","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:59:28.332Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:59 GMT-5] C:\\Windows\\System32> schtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"cmd.exe /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\" /F\nSUCCESS: The scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" has successfully been created."}],"timestamp":1774389568326}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f2680e2","parentId":"1b1fa5a2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:59:36.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfecto. **Ya quedГі creada**.\n\nAhora haz estas dos pruebas:\n\n## 1. Probarla manualmente\nEn CMD admin:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\"\n```\n\n## 2. Verificar estado del gateway\nLuego:\n\n```bat\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n## QuГ© queremos confirmar\nQue bajo **SYSTEM** sГӯ logra arrancar el gateway bien.\n\n## Si funciona\nEntonces ya quedas con:\n- BIOS enciende PC\n- Task Scheduler corre al startup\n- OpenClaw gateway arranca sin depender del login\n\n## Si no funciona\nNo pasa nada: la tarea ya existe, y el siguiente paso serГӯa ajustar el comando para el contexto SYSTEM.\n\nPero por ahora: **bien, ya quedГі montado.**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30947da048191bf5b66a018b9416a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":323,"output":173,"cacheRead":99456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99952,"cost":{"input":0.0008075000000000001,"output":0.002595,"cacheRead":0.024863999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028266499999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389568332,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30943c14881919009fdbfef689762"}}
{"type":"message","id":"696ab2b6","parentId":"4f2680e2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:59:57.674Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 16:59:50 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 16:59:54 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 16:59 GMT-5] Microsoft Windows [Version 10.0.26100.3476] (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved. C:\\Windows\\System32> schtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"cmd.exe /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\" /F SUCCESS: The scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" has successfully been created. C:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" SUCCESS: Attempted to run the scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\". C:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /FO LIST Folder: \\ HostName: DESKTOP-24HIUD3 TaskName: \\OpenClaw Gateway Startup Next Run Time: N/A Status: Ready Logon Mode: Interactive/Background Last Run Time: 3/24/2026 4:59:44 PM Last Result: 1 Author: DESKTOP-24HIUD3\\Gustavo Task To Run: cmd.exe /c C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd Start In: N/A Comment: N/A Scheduled Task State: Enabled Idle Time: Disabled Power Management: Stop On Battery Mode, No Start On Batteries Run As User: SYSTEM Delete Task If Not Rescheduled: Disabled Stop Task If Runs X Hours and X Mins: 72:00:00 Schedule: Scheduling data is not available in this format. Schedule Type: At system start up Start Time: N/A Start Date: N/A End Date: N/A Days: N/A Months: N/A Repeat: Every: N/A Repeat: Until: Time: N/A Repeat: Until: Duration: N/A Repeat: Stop If Still Running: N/A C:\\Windows\\System32>"}],"timestamp":1774389597667}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca1febd9","parentId":"696ab2b6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:00:10.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Bien: **la tarea sГӯ corre, pero fallГі**.\n\nLa pista clave es esta:\n\n- **Last Result: `1`**\n\nEso significa que el comando arrancГі pero **terminГі con error**.\n\n## Mi lectura\nBajo **SYSTEM**, `gateway.cmd` probablemente no estГЎ encontrando bien:\n- entorno de usuario\n- ruta base\n- o algo dentro de `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw`\n\n## Lo siguiente a probar\nHaz una versiГіn mГЎs explГӯcita del comando, usando `cmd /d /c` y cambiando al directorio correcto.\n\nPrimero borra la tarea:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Delete /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /F\n```\n\nLuego crГ©ala asГӯ:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"cmd.exe /d /c cd /d C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw && gateway.cmd\" /F\n```\n\n## Por quГ© mejor\nPorque:\n- entra al directorio correcto\n- ejecuta el script desde ahГӯ\n- evita algunos problemas de contexto\n\n## Si `&&` te da pelea en schtasks\nusa esta alternativa:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"cmd.exe /d /c \\\"cd /d C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw && gateway.cmd\\\"\" /F\n```\n\n## Luego\nprueba otra vez:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\"\nschtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /V /FO LIST\n```\n\n## QuГ© queremos ver\nQue **Last Result** pase idealmente a:\n- `0`\n\nSi quieres, despuГ©s de que lo corras, me pegas el resultado y lo ajustamos fino.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c309658c308191b29c1968373733d0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":636,"output":414,"cacheRead":99840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100890,"cost":{"input":0.00159,"output":0.00621,"cacheRead":0.02496,"cacheWrite":