{"type":"message","id":"d155d8bd","parentId":"ca1febd9","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:01:27.543Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 17:00:54 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 17:00:57 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 17:01 GMT-5] C:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Delete /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /F\nSUCCESS: The scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" was successfully deleted.\n\nC:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"cmd.exe /d /c cd /d C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw && gateway.cmd\" /F\nSUCCESS: The scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" has successfully been created.\n\nC:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\"\nSUCCESS: Attempted to run the scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\".\n\nC:\\Windows\\System32>"}],"timestamp":1774389687537}}
{"type":"message","id":"e475a940","parentId":"d155d8bd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:01:34.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Bien. Ahora falta la verificaciГіn.\n\nCorre esto:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /V /FO LIST\n```\n\ny fГӯjate en:\n- **Last Result**\n\n## Lo ideal\n- `Last Result: 0`\n\n## Si sigue en `1`\nentonces el siguiente ajuste serГӯa envolver todo mejor o llamar el `.cmd` por ruta absoluta completa.\n\nTambiГ©n puedes revisar en paralelo:\n\n```bat\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\nSi el gateway sale como arriba, entonces aunque la tarea no te muestre bonito, ya nos sirve.\n\nPГ©game:\n- **Last Result**\n- y si quieres tambiГ©n `openclaw gateway status`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c309bd94dc8191b67bde23a2ad1588\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":447,"output":152,"cacheRead":100736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101335,"cost":{"input":0.0011175,"output":0.00228,"cacheRead":0.025183999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0285815}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389687543,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c309bb02d081919804748a3929d800"}}
{"type":"message","id":"60cf7d23","parentId":"e475a940","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:01:44.504Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 17:01 GMT-5] C:\\Windows\\System32> schtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /FO LIST Folder: \\ HostName: DESKTOP-24HIUD3 TaskName: \\OpenClaw Gateway Startup Next Run Time: N/A Status: Ready Logon Mode: Interactive/Background Last Run Time: 3/24/2026 5:01:20 PM Last Result: 1 Author: DESKTOP-24HIUD3\\Gustavo Task To Run: cmd.exe /d /c cd /d C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw && gateway.cmd Start In: N/A Comment: N/A Scheduled Task State: Enabled Idle Time: Disabled Power Management: Stop On Battery Mode, No Start On Batteries Run As User: SYSTEM Delete Task If Not Rescheduled: Disabled Stop Task If Runs X Hours and X Mins: 72:00:00 Schedule: Scheduling data is not available in this format. Schedule Type: At system start up Start Time: N/A Start Date: N/A End Date: N/A Days: N/A Months: N/A Repeat: Every: N/A Repeat: Until: Time: N/A Repeat: Until: Duration: N/A Repeat: Stop If Still Running: N/A"}],"timestamp":1774389704500}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0dc0604","parentId":"60cf7d23","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:01:58.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sigue fallando bajo **SYSTEM**.\n\nLa conclusiГіn Гәtil es esta:\n\n## QuГ© significa\n- la tarea sГӯ se dispara\n- pero `gateway.cmd` **no corre bien en contexto SYSTEM**\n\nEso suele pasar porque el script depende de:\n- tu perfil de usuario\n- variables de entorno de usuario\n- o sesiГіn interactiva\n\n## Siguiente intento bueno\nProbar con la ruta absoluta del wrapper y sin depender de `cd`.\n\nBorra y recrea asГӯ:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Delete /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /F\n```\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"\\\"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\\\"\" /F\n```\n\n## Si eso no deja\nusa esta variante:\n\n```bat\nschtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\" /F\n```\n\n## Y luego prueba\n```bat\nschtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\"\nschtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /V /FO LIST\n```\n\n## Si vuelve a dar `1`\nya te dirГӯa algo claro:\n- **SYSTEM no es la ruta correcta para este gateway**\n- y tocarГӯa usar:\n  - inicio de sesiГіn automГЎtico + Startup\n  **o**\n  - tarea al logon de Gustavo\n\n## Mi lectura honesta\nEstamos ya en el punto donde probablemente:\n- **OpenClaw gateway fue pensado para usuario interactivo**\nmГЎs que para `SYSTEM`.\n\nPrueba esa Гәltima variante directa y si vuelve a `1`, te digo la soluciГіn final sin seguir dando vueltas.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c309d2be5c81918ff2909b527271f6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":101671,"output":390,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102061,"cost":{"input":0.2541775,"output":0.00585,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.2600275}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389704504,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c309cbf4e081919160c5d7a2667ab7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b68b9856","parentId":"d0dc0604","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:02:47.872Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 17:01:57 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 17:02:01 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 17:02 GMT-5] C:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Delete /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /F SUCCESS: The scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" was successfully deleted. C:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Create /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /SC ONSTART /RU SYSTEM /RL HIGHEST /TR \"\\\"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\\\"\" /F SUCCESS: The scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" has successfully been created. C:\\Windows\\System32>schtasks /Run /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" SUCCESS: Attempted to run the scheduled task \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\". C:\\Windows\\System32> schtasks /Query /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway Startup\" /FO LIST Folder: \\ HostName: DESKTOP-24HIUD3 TaskName: \\OpenClaw Gateway Startup Next Run Time: N/A Status: Running Logon Mode: Interactive/Background Last Run Time: 3/24/2026 5:02:42 PM Last Result: 267009 Author: DESKTOP-24HIUD3\\Gustavo Task To Run: \"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\" Start In: N/A Comment: N/A Scheduled Task State: Enabled Idle Time: Disabled Power Management: Stop On Battery Mode, No Start On Batteries Run As User: SYSTEM Delete Task If Not Rescheduled: Disabled Stop Task If Runs X Hours and X Mins: 72:00:00 Schedule: Scheduling data is not available in this format. Schedule Type: At system start up Start Time: N/A Start Date: N/A End Date: N/A Days: N/A Months: N/A Repeat: Every: N/A Repeat: Until: Time: N/A Repeat: Until: Duration: N/A Repeat: Stop If Still Running: N/A"}],"timestamp":177438976