{"type":"message","id":"e3dc63de","parentId":"b68b9856","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:03:00.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Eso ya se ve **mucho mejor**.\n\n## Lo importante\nAhora tienes:\n\n- **Status:** `Running`\n- **Run As User:** `SYSTEM`\n\nEso significa que **sГӯ estГЎ arrancando**.\n\n## Sobre `Last Result: 267009`\nNo me preocupa demasiado mientras el estado actual sea **Running**.  \nEn tareas que lanzan procesos persistentes/wrappers, a veces ese valor no refleja вҖңfallГівҖқ, sino cГіmo quedГі el handoff del proceso.\n\n## Lo que toca validar ahora\nHaz esto:\n\n```bat\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n## Si sale bien\nEntonces ya quedГі:\n- PC enciende\n- Task Scheduler corre al startup\n- gateway arranca como SYSTEM\n- no dependes del login\n\n## Mi lectura actual\n**Ya casi lo tienes resuelto.**  \nLa seГұal fuerte aquГӯ es **Status: Running**.\n\nPГ©game solo el resultado de:\n\n```bat\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\ny te digo si lo damos por cerrado.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30a1284fc81919d1bdb606f36d307\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":54408,"output":218,"cacheRead":47616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102242,"cost":{"input":0.13602,"output":0.00327,"cacheRead":0.011904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.151194}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389767873,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30a0d61188191a39302b88d7de8df"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68601399","parentId":"e3dc63de","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:03:20.472Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 17:03:01 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-03-24 17:03:05 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 17:03 GMT-5] C:\\Windows\\System32>openclaw gateway status\n\nрҹҰһ OpenClaw 2026.3.23-1 (unknown) вҖ” I don't sleep, I just enter low-power mode and dream of clean diffs.\n\n|\no\nService: Scheduled Task (registered)\nFile logs: ~\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\openclaw\\openclaw-2026-03-24.log\nCommand: C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789\nService file: ~\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\nConfig (cli): ~\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=18789 (service args)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\nProbe note: Loopback-only gateway; only local clients can connect.\n\nRuntime: running (pid 18736, Startup-folder login item installed; listener detected on port 18789.)\nRPC probe: ok\n\nListening: 127.0.0.1:18789\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting"}],"timestamp":1774389800467}}
{"type":"message","id":"15784462","parentId":"68601399","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:03:29.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ. **Ya quedГі funcionando.**\n\nLa lГӯnea clave es:\n\n- **Runtime: running**\n- **RPC probe: ok**\n- **Listening: 127.0.0.1:18789**\n\n## TraducciГіn\nEl gateway:\n- estГЎ arriba\n- responde\n- estГЎ escuchando en el puerto correcto\n- y el probe lo confirma\n\n## En corto\n**Lo damos por cerrado.**\n\nTu flujo quedГі asГӯ:\n- BIOS enciende el PC\n- Scheduled Task lanza OpenClaw\n- gateway queda corriendo\n\n## Un detalle curioso\n`gateway status` tambiГ©n detecta:\n- **Startup-folder login item installed**\n\nO sea que probablemente tienes **las dos cosas**:\n- tarea programada\n- y arranque por carpeta Startup\n\n## Mi recomendaciГіn\nPara no duplicar arranques, deja **solo uno** como estГЎndar.\n\nComo ya te funcionГі el de **Scheduled Task / ONSTART / SYSTEM**, yo me quedarГӯa con ese y quitarГӯa el de Startup si tambiГ©n estГЎ activo.\n\nSi quieres, te digo cГіmo limpiar el duplicado y dejar un solo camino correcto.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30a2f7e1c8191aa5c249439d30c4c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":54551,"output":236,"cacheRead":47616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102403,"cost":{"input":0.1363775,"output":0.00354,"cacheRead":0.011904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1518215}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389800472,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30a2bf0708191a8a961aacf64791b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fed998ab","parentId":"15784462","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:04:02.129Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 17:04 GMT-5] ya guardaste como comunicarte con notion ? para que lo tengas en ceunta en futuras sesiones ?"}],"timestamp":1774389842125}}
