{"type":"message","id":"cd47773b","parentId":"cc1641cc","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:04:43.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ. **Ya quedГі guardado para futuras sesiones**.\n\nGuardГ©:\n- en `workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- y mГЎs detallado en `workspace/notion-integration-notes.md`\n\n## QuГ© quedГі recordado\n- que **sГӯ hay integraciГіn usable con Notion**\n- que se usa vГӯa **API oficial**\n- que el token estГЎ en **`NOTION_TOKEN`**\n- que la pГЎgina principal es **`Atlas OS`**\n- cГіmo buscar, leer, aГұadir y archivar bloques\n- y que PowerShell puede romper emojis/encoding, asГӯ que a veces conviene texto limpio\n\nY quedГі **commiteado**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30a7b86948191b3f7be88aca8eb7c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":198,"output":140,"cacheRead":101888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102226,"cost":{"input":0.000495,"output":0.0021,"cacheRead":0.025471999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028066999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774389873131,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30a78fdb8819197757a8d2a0b7394"}}
