{"type":"message","id":"96bd5630","parentId":"167ffe4f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:14:55.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo.\n\nYa quedГі:\n\n## Guardado en memoria\n- revisar diariamente `atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com`\n- detectar reenvГӯos, pendientes y plazos\n- recordarte por WhatsApp al:\n  - **`+573183718246`**\n- incluir deadlines cercanos\n\nTambiГ©n guardГ© el ejemplo vigente:\n- **desde hoy tienes 3 dГӯas para hacer el challenge de ZooLATECH**\n\n## Automatizado\nTe programГ© un cron diario a las **8:00 AM** para eso.\n\n**Job:**\n- `daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder`\n\n**ID:**\n- `b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c`\n\nY quedГі **commiteado**.\n\n## Ojo\nAhora mismo tienes **dos jobs a las 8:00 AM**:\n- revisiГіn de **Atlas OS / Notion**\n- revisiГіn de **correo + reminder por WhatsApp**\n\nEso no estГЎ mal, pero si quieres luego los unifico en una sola rutina matutina mГЎs elegante.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30cddf720819195b71962186bdf69\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":179,"output":230,"cacheRead":103424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103833,"cost":{"input":0.00044750000000000004,"output":0.00345,"cacheRead":0.025856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029753500000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774390488401,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30cdc1e78819189d618b169b61089"}}
