{"type":"message","id":"3931fa43","parentId":"20cbdab8","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:15:44.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SГӯ, se puede, pero primero corrijo un detalle:\n\nPusiste:\n- `toledo970501@gmal.com`\n\nВҝQuieres decir:\n- **`toledo970501@gmail.com`**?\n\n## Y el flujo quedarГӯa\nAdemГЎs del recordatorio por WhatsApp:\n- crear/enviar invitaciГіn o evento al correo:\n  - **`toledo970501@gmail.com`**\npara que te aparezca en tu calendario\n\n## Ojo importante\nEso ya implica:\n- **crear eventos**\n- y **enviarlos**\nque sГӯ es acciГіn externa real\n\nYo lo puedo hacer, pero prefiero confirmarte el correo exacto antes de dejarlo automatizado.\n\nRespГіndeme solo:\n- **sГӯ, es gmail.com**  \no\n- corrГӯgeme el correo exacto.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30d0f583081919d04b0e1af1e64d4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":305,"output":174,"cacheRead":103680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104159,"cost":{"input":0.0007625,"output":0.00261,"cacheRead":0.02592,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0292925}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774390537412,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30d0d0c6081919b97b851da1f6145"}}
