{"type":"message","id":"24ac640d","parentId":"527eb291","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:19:56.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo.\n\nYa quedГі asГӯ:\n\n## 8:00 AM\nEl cron de la maГұana ahora:\n- revisa `atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com`\n- detecta pendientes y deadlines\n- **organiza lo relevante en calendario**\n  hacia **`toledo970501@gmail.com`**\n- y ademГЎs te manda resumen por WhatsApp a:\n  - **`+573183718246`**\n\n## 7:00 PM\nTe creГ© otro cron para:\n- revisar pendientes no resueltos\n- ver quГ© pasa para maГұana\n- detectar deadlines cercanos\n- **organizar lo relevante en calendario**\n  hacia **`toledo970501@gmail.com`**\n- y mandarte el paneo nocturno por WhatsApp\n\n## IDs\n- **8:00 AM:** `b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c`\n- **7:00 PM:** `8157ed89-ee52-482d-a791-31181c4fff11`\n\n## TambiГ©n\nLo dejГ© guardado en memoria como cadencia oficial:\n- **8 AM**\n- **7 PM**\n- WhatsApp + calendario\n\nY quedГі **commiteado**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30e0841908191913215e8ef1f7d73\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":174,"output":262,"cacheRead":108416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108852,"cost":{"input":0.00043500000000000006,"output":0.00393,"cacheRead":0.027104,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031469}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774390784840,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30e04a84481918fe65dc9f4695651"}}
